article.description: — Tyon Grant-Foster and Jovan Blacksher Jr. scored 18 points apiece to help Grand Canyon defeat Southern Utah 94-65 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Grant-Foster, Blacksher lead Grand Canyon over Southern Utah 94-65
article.linkText: Grant-Foster, Blacksher lead Grand Canyon over Southern Utah 94-65
article.story: PHOENIX -- — Tyon Grant-Foster and Jovan Blacksher Jr. scored 18 points apiece to help Grand Canyon defeat Southern Utah 94-65 on Saturday night. Grant-Foster added seven rebounds for the Antelopes (22-2, 12-1 Western Athletic Conference). Blacksher added three steals. Lok Wur had 10 points. Dominique Ford led the Thunderbirds (9-15, 4-9) with 23 points. Prophet Johnson added 12 points. Brock Felder had eight points and three blocks. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
